content.text: Hey! How's it going?
Hi there! It's going well, thanks for asking!
That's good to hear! What are you up to today?
Not much, just hanging out with my husband and our dog.
That sounds fun! I'm just getting ready to go to work. I'm a waitress.
Oh, that's cool! I've never been a waitress, but I've always thought it would be fun.
It can be, but it's also a lot of work!
I bet! What do you like most about it?
I like getting to meet new people and make their day a little brighter.
That's a great quality to have! My husband is a firefighter, and he loves making people's lives better.
That's so awesome! I'm sure he's a great firefighter.
He is! I'm so lucky to have him in my life.
That's great! I'm glad to hear that.
Thanks! What's your favorite band?
My favorite band is Kesha!
Oh, cool! I've never heard of her. What kind of music does she make?
She makes pop music, but it's a little different than most pop music. It's more fun and upbeat.
That sounds cool! I'll have to check her out.
You should! I think you'd like her.
Thanks for the recommendation!
No problem! I'm always happy to share my music with people.
